   "source": [
    "# Sales Forecasting — Baseline+\n",
    "**Goal:** Predict daily `Revenue` and `COGS` for 2023-01-01 → 2024-07-01 using historical data (2012–2022).\n",
    "\n",
    "**Strategy (improved baseline):**\n",
    "1. Build a recency-weighted seasonal profile by **(month, day)**.\n",
    "2. Estimate YoY growth and calibrate damping on a validation tail (2021–2022).\n",
    "3. Add weekday + promotion/holiday/Tet residual adjustments.\n",
    "4. Backtest quickly, then export submission.\n",
    "\n",
    "**ML sections (from Section 8):**\n",
    "- Use selected features: `output/train_features_selected.csv`, `output/test_features_selected.csv`.\n",
    "- Log transform on Revenue only: `Revenue_log = log(Revenue + 1)` (COGS stays raw). section 8"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "id": "8a1fce39",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "## 1 — Imports & Config"
   ]
  },
